{"tid":617030,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"報道：滙控或收縮環球業務版圖","createTime":"2018-04-04T16:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T12:06:01.000Z","uid":70274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f072a14bf136f7fa4a8a28925d9ba98fec2e3250","tid":617030,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"香港電台-財經<br />\n<br />\n彭博報道，匯控新任行政總裁范寧與主席杜嘉祺有意進一步收縮環球業務版圖。<br />\n報道引述消息人士說，在67個集團經營的地區中，范寧對其中四分之一正進行檢討，並且考慮可能退出或出售規模較小的零售業務，例如百慕達、馬耳他同烏拉圭。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士說，雖然有關市場仍錄得盈利，但范寧同杜嘉祺希望加速建立亞洲為重心，減省外圍業務，特別是在零售銀行業務方面削減成本。<br />\n另外，范寧亦打算擴大財富及資產管理業務，包括成立獨立部門。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/報道-滙控或收縮環球業務版圖-140538501.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Ffinance%2F%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93-%E6%BB%99%E6%8E%A7%E6%88%96%E6%94%B6%E7%B8%AE%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99%E7%89%88%E5%9C%96-140538501.html&d=%2Bizxg92NueXeRQa%2BSPevUNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d02d1b18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/報道-滙控或收縮環球業務版圖-140538501.html</a>"},{"pid":"323d0b26b4e8be3a068751e8d243c06203be18df","tid":617030,"uid":51753,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T02:15:51.000Z","msg":"講完一輪即係準備炒幾多隻IT狗"},{"pid":"e38f57e3e2b0239d94f818ccfddb13559280f031","tid":617030,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"323d0b26b4e8be3a068751e8d243c06203be18df","tid":617030,"uid":51753,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T02:15:51.000Z","msg":"講完一輪即係準備炒幾多隻IT狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3034c566267e3b106f3ae0fa4de430499449340d","tid":617030,"uid":58413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci